data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom ranch home in the Olde Liberty Golf Club Community featuring an 18-hole championship golf course, pool, and athletic center. This home offers a blend of spaciousness and functionality with an open living concept, converted garage multipurpose room, updated kitchen, and covered back deck. The timeless exterior leads to a light-filled living area seamlessly connecting with dining and kitchen spaces. The updated kitchen is a chef's delight with modern appliances and ample granite counter space. A standout feature is the huge converted garage, a versatile space for a home office, game room, gym, or home theater. Step outside to a covered back deck for al fresco dining and relaxation in the landscaped backyard. The spacious owners suite with bathroom along with three additional bedrooms provide comfort and flexibility. This home has been beautifully maintained and ready to move in.
